                <h2 data-uuid="deb21ae7a8ba4b8f9196f05a1c432587"> Essential Question–Writing</h2>
                <p class="white" data-uuid="277d0fb2dc2f4beea5f19e926fb8c6aa">In this module you’ve
                    learned about the civilizations and societies that existed in the Americas, Africa,
                    and Europe before 1500. Now it’s your turn to demonstrate your understanding of
                    the module content by writing an essay.</p>
            </div>
            <h3 data-uuid="1f94a78b3bdd48dcaad5e972349f0c8a">Why might a U.S. historian study the Americas, Africa, and Europe before 1500?</h3>
            <p data-uuid="57d11459074a4edca8b508e2e70a1e2f">Write a persuasive essay
                answering this question. Your essay should include key people, events, and
                turning points in the histories of each world region. Be sure to cite evidence
                to support your position and organize your essay into an introduction, body,
                and conclusion.</p>
        </section>
